The nature of the study skills and their development. Study Regulation, Study Information System. Active learning.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to support students' study skills for learning at the unversity. This course helps to develop different learning communites.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  The student develop the basic knowledge of study skills and how to support these skills. As a result of successful studies of this course the student will:  1. analyze himself as a learner and based on the analysis design a plan for improving his study skills, 2. plan his studies at the university according to the study system specifics,  3. use the basic principles of citing and references used in institute of education, 4. analyze and use social skills in different learning experiences, 5. use appropriate learning strategies in academic assignments.
